Package: HiCExperiment
Title: Interface to (m)cool files in R
Version: 0.98.0
Date: 2022-11-10
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Jacques",
           family = "Serizay",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jacquesserizay@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4295-0624")))
Description: R interface to (m)cool files and other Hi-C processed file formats.
    `.(m)cool` and `.pairs` files can be directly parsed and subsetted to create 
    HiCExperiment objects, allowing a memory-efficient representation of 
    Hi-C data in R. 
